#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "Click **Unlock**."
msgstr "Feu clic a **Desbloqueja**."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "   *Unlock VeraCrypt Volumes* unlocks your volume.\n"
msgstr "   *Desbloqueja els volums de VeraCrypt* desbloqueja el vostre volum.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"   If unlocking the volume fails (for example, if you mistyped the\n"
"   password), click on **Unlock** to try\n"
